title: Nomination Sent to the Senate | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
December 15, 2010

 



Nomination Sent to the Senate





	Clyde E. Terry, of New Hampshire, to be a Member of the National Council on Disability for a term expiring September 17, 2013, vice John R. Vaughn, resigned.
